Frequently Asked Questions

What payment methods do you accept?

We accept all major credit cards (Visa, Mastercard, Amex, Discover), PayPal, Apple Pay, and Google Pay. Organizations can request purchase orders and Net 30 terms.

What's your refund policy?

We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee on all digital products, no questions asked. For workshop bookings, cancellations must be made 14 days before the event for a full refund.

How do I access my purchases?

After purchase, you'll receive immediate access via email with download links. All purchases include lifetime access and future updates for 2 years.

Do you offer educational discounts?

Yes! We offer 15% off for non-profits, 25% off for schools/universities buying 10+ licenses, and 20% off for community centers and clinics. Contact us for a custom quote.

Can I share my purchase with others?

Individual licenses are for personal use. For team/organizational use, please purchase our Enterprise License or contact us for bulk licensing options.

Can I try before I buy?

Absolutely! We offer free previews of everything: Chapters 1-2 of the ebook, sample lesson plans, first 5 slides of workshop presentations, and the complete FREE interactive app.
